  <description>
    <p>
      Simple Prayer/Adhan Times App.


      Prayer times are getting fetched every month from Türkiye&apos;s Diyanet İşleri Başkanlığı (Presidency of Religious Affairs).


      Network Permission: Fetching prayer times from internet.


      Microphone/Audio Permission: Play notification sound when X minutes left. No microphone access. 
    </p>
  </description>

